Package org.akubraproject.rmi.remote

The Akubra RMI rpc definitions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
RemoteBlob Represents a blob on the remote server.
RemoteBlobCreator An interface that lets clients write to an output stream on a remote server to create a new blob.
RemoteCallListener A listener for calls that the server side wishes to make on the client side.
RemoteCallListener.Operation<T> An operation to be performed on the client side.
RemoteConnection Represents a connection to a blob-store on a remote server.
RemoteInputStream Represents an input stream on remote.
RemoteIterator<T extends Serializable> The interface to support an Iterator backed by items on a remote server.
RemoteOutputStream An interface that lets clients write to an output stream on a remote server.
RemoteStore Represents a remote blob store.
RemoteSynchronization Represents a JTA Synchronization listener on the server side.
RemoteTransactionListener A listener for calls made on a Transaction object.
RemoteXAResource Represents an XA Resource on tha akubra server side.
 

Class Summary
PartialBuffer Represents the parameters of OutputStream.write(byte[], int, int) call.
RemoteCallListener.Result<T> Result of an operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.DelistXAResource Encapsulates a Transaction.delistResource(javax.transaction.xa.XAResource, int) operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.EnlistXAResource Encapsulates an Transaction.enlistResource(javax.transaction.xa.XAResource) operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.GetStatus Encapsulates a Transaction.getStatus() operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.RegisterSynchronization Encapsulates a Transaction.registerSynchronization(javax.transaction.Synchronization) operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.Rollback Encapsulates a Transaction.rollback() operation.
RemoteTransactionListener.XAResourceOp<T> Abstract base class for operations involving an XAResource.
SerializedXid A serializable copy for non serializable xids so that they can be send across RMI.
